#### Text 3 (深度阅读与时间管理)
*That everyone's too busy these days is a cliché...*

**31. The usual time-management techniques don't work because _______.**
- [ ] A. what they can offer does not ease the modern mind
- [ ] B. what challenging books demand is repetitive reading
- [ ] C. what people often forget is carrying a book with them
- [ ] D. what deep reading requires cannot be guaranteed

<details>
<summary>✅ 点击查看答案与解析</summary>

**答案：D**
**解析：** 细节题。第二段指出深度阅读需要 "a special kind of time"，这种时间不能仅靠提高效率获得 (can't be obtained merely by becoming more efficient)，即普通技巧无法保证深度阅读所需的条件。
</details>

**32. The "empty bottles" metaphor illustrates that people feel a pressure to _______.**
- [ ] A. update their to-do lists
- [ ] B. make passing time fulfilling
- [ ] C. carry their plans through
- [ ] D. pursue carefree reading

<details>
<summary>✅ 点击查看答案与解析</summary>

**答案：B**
**解析：** 细节题。第三段提到人们感到压力要去 "fill these different-sized bottles"，意思是让流逝的时间变得充实 (fulfilling)，否则就是浪费。
</details>

**33. Eberle would agree that scheduling regular times for reading helps _______.**
- [ ] A. encourage the efficiency mind-set
- [ ] B. develop online reading habits
- [ ] C. promote ritualistic reading
- [ ] D. achieve immersive reading

<details>
<summary>✅ 点击查看答案与解析</summary>

**答案：D**
**解析：** 细节题。第四段提到这种仪式化行为帮助我们进入 "soul time"，即沉浸式阅读 (immersive reading)。
</details>

**34. "Carry a book with you at all times" can work if _______.**
- [ ] A. reading becomes your primary business of the day
- [ ] B. all the daily business has been promptly dealt with
- [ ] C. you are able to drop back to business after reading
- [ ] D. time can be evenly split for reading and business

<details>
<summary>✅ 点击查看答案与解析</summary>

**答案：A**
**解析：** 细节题。第四段提到前提是 "reading becomes the default state"（阅读成为默认状态），即阅读成为你一天的主要事务，偶尔浮出水面处理杂事。
</details>

**35. The best title for this text could be _______.**
- [ ] A. How to Enjoy Easy Reading
- [ ] B. How to Find Time to Read
- [ ] C. How to Set Reading Goals
- [ ] D. How to Read Extensively

<details>
<summary>✅ 点击查看答案与解析</summary>

**答案：B**
**解析：** 主旨题。文章从 "没时间读书" 的抱怨入手，分析了普通时间管理无效的原因，并提出了找到深度阅读时间的具体方法，故 [B] 最贴切。
</details>

